  • Method Details

    • fillInterested

      public void fillInterested()

      Registers read interest using the default Callback with Invocable.InvocationType.NON_BLOCKING.

      When read readiness is signaled, AbstractConnection.onFillable() or AbstractConnection.onFillInterestedFailed(Throwable) will be invoked.

      This method should be used sparingly, and AbstractConnection.fillInterested(Callback) should be preferred instead, passing a Callback that specifies the Invocable.InvocationType for each specific case where read interest needs to be registered.

      Overrides:
      fillInterested in class AbstractConnection
